import "./sm.css" export default function Sm11() { return (

Your subconscious mind as a partner in success

  • The infinite intelligence of my subconscious mind reveals to me my true place in life
  • Specialise in some particular branch of work and know more about it than anyone else
  • Make a living, get by is not true success - man’s motive must be greater truer and altruistic
  • Your idea for success should benefit humanity and it should serve the success of the world
  • There is no success without peace of mind
  • A successful person loves his work and expresses him fully
  • The secret of success is to see your project in completion.
  • A successful man is not selfish his main desire in life is to serve humanity
  • The idea of success contains all elements of success, repeat to yourself the word “success” frequently with conviction and you will be under a subconscious compulsion to succeed
) }
